<C>__{jill}
<D>__{forty minutes?}
<C>__{maitre d' }
<D>__{that's right.}
<C>__{jill}
<P>__{(after a beat)}
<D>__{okay. thank you.}
<A>__{she hangs up, thinks for a moment, then picks up the phone again and dials "o"...}
<C>__{operator }
<D>__{operator...}
