<C>__{man's voice }
<D>__{seventh precinct, sergeant sacker.}
<C>__{jill}
<D>__{hello, i've been getting phone calls, every fifteen minutes or so. i think it's a man. he's trying to scare me.}
<C>__{sacker }
<D>__{an anonymous caller?}
<C>__{jill}
<D>__{that's right.}
<C>__{sacker }
<D>__{has he threatened you?}
<C>__{jill}
<D>__{no.}
<C>__{sacker }
<D>__{has he been using obscene language?}
<C>__{jill}
<D>__{no. he just keeps calling me. sometimes he doesn't say anything.}
<C>__{sacker }
<D>__{there's really nothing we can do about it down here. is the phone listed in your name?}
<C>__{jill}
<D>__{no, i'm just the babysitter.}
<C>__{sacker }
<D>__{it's probably just some weirdo. the city's full of them. believe it or not, we get reports like this every night. it's nothing to worry about.}
<C>__{jill}
<D>__{oh...}
